10/ Why buy a Starcatcher?
Art is simply one of the best in the space and founders locked up a big portion of the minting revenue. Who doesn't love a team that is comitted to building something long term? https://t.co/Xo1eiXDyok

These cuties round up the post perfectally. What more needs to be said, just take a look for yourself. https://t.co/sGGHefW8N1

6/ Here are just a few I found by browsing the collection. This makes for a really fun experience when looking for a starcatcher. (twitter wont let me post a bunch of gifs so look for these traits if you want to see what it looks like) https://t.co/KP6AIqjitd

5/ Body
Lost for words looking at the different traits for the body. There is really something for everyone. Fun, good looking & clean art all the way. On top of everything to choose from, there are animated ones too. https://t.co/qZlQd5mBdM

4/ This makes for a very nice variations of the same animated trait. 
What about the backgrounds without "bling"?
Theres a big selection to pick from and really makes your starcatcher pop. Here are a few just looking at floor. https://t.co/q5Lq3svbDE

3/ Backgrounds. 
Scrolling through the collection you will notice that the background game is nothing that should be overlooked, and @Beutrec definitely didn't. On top of the amazing backgrounds there is also "Bling" which are animated traits added on top of the background. https://t.co/TEnBb9MS91
